pageContext.claim: “In recent weeks we have met with large numbers of Democrat lawmakers to hear their ideas and suggestions. By incorporating the priorities of rank and file Democrats in our plan, we hope they will offer their enthusiastic support.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump met with only a handful of Democrats, who says they told him to reopen the government before negotiations could begin. The elements he outlined as an offer attract virtually no Democratic support, as they were considered temporary solutions to problems caused by administration actions.
